{"tid":2279572,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"一直臨摹/描圖係唔會學識畫畫?","createTime":"2020-11-10T01:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T09:46:21.000Z","uid":137768,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"58c76f44ba658ee83a0b45b640661237df140a70","tid":2279572,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T01:14:26.000Z","msg":"事源好耐買左塊畫板<br />\n最近終於的起心肝想試下畫啲圖玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但因為新手黎畫得好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就上網dl左張圖放喺底試下照畫下<br />\n雖然效果都係怪怪地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但諗緊咁樣畫法係咪其實學唔到野<br />\n下面有圖 感覺都係奇奇怪怪咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求大家指點迷津一下有咩途徑練習<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想畫漫畫角色多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e23b10af27f638977c5e53fedbf61aaa7db9b0","tid":2279572,"uid":49004,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T01:19:05.000Z","msg":"明日香<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f51756a5528d5afb54c392d3c32792f5d7e92311","tid":2279572,"uid":210612,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T01:20:10.000Z","msg":"咁睇你係用手臨摹定係用腦臨摹"},{"pid":"2c8b1e187b7c6493d2656b7222f7ac1171c5a198","tid":2279572,"uid":69071,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T01:21:49.000Z","msg":"識畫畫要講創作，臨幕叻只可以講你畫畫水平高。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比啲信心自己畫吓心目中理想嘅角色，久而久之就會創作到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24404aa58a51aee4eec264b8a0a7ced56465d101","tid":2279572,"uid":380266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T01:22:45.000Z","msg":"冇錢電繪，唯有素描"},{"pid":"d3cea808f5005e117eb2b2df72586e883c11c2ab","tid":2279572,"uid":240499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T01:23:04.000Z","msg":"小學時候有個同學畫漫畫超靚，佢教我都係放本漫畫喺下面印住咁畫練出黎，我試過一段時間，失敗咗，結論係睇你自己既資質 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"618c3e43d1a3d1322a87e51b1909149de85213bf","tid":2279572,"uid":380266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c8b1e187b7c6493d2656b7222f7ac1171c5a198","tid":2279572,"uid":69071,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T01:21:49.000Z","msg":"識畫畫要講創作，臨幕叻只可以講你畫畫水平高。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比啲信心自己畫吓心目中理想嘅角色，久而久之就會創作到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T01:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7230ac9752f6d7fde928168cde5fb97c59592bc3","tid":2279572,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f51756a5528d5afb54c392d3c32792f5d7e92311","tid":2279572,"uid":210612,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T01:20:10.000Z","msg":"咁睇你係用手臨摹定係用腦臨摹"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T01:25:52.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"09b0046fd4118497e37aae576b1cb272a0842b98","tid":2279572,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f51756a5528d5afb54c392d3c32792f5d7e92311","tid":2279572,"uid":210612,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T01:20:10.000Z","msg":"咁睇你係用手臨摹定係用腦臨摹"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T01:31:52.000Z","msg":"兩者有咩差別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc05bdf2bd2460935128ccf748e6efaf52bc78ed","tid":2279572,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24404aa58a51aee4eec264b8a0